### continer
 Docker is one of the most popular continer technology.

 Docker = { container (webserver(Lib+Dep))} + { container (Database(Lib+Dep))} + { container (messaging(Lib+Dep))} + { container (orchestratoin(Lib+Dep))}

 Continers = Isolation {(own process) + (own newwork) + (own maounts)}

 Types of contianer = LXC LXD LXCFS LXCRI

 Docker utilizes LXC container.

 LXC features = kernel namespaces (ipc,uts,mount,pid,network,user) , Apparmor/SELinux profile, Seccomp policies, Kernel capabilities, CGroups (control gropups).

 Docker Image = Docker container1 + Docker container2 + Docker contaier 3
(template)             (running instances)

